item.comments: I didn't realize I was moved up automatically. I have made other plans but let me see if I can arrange it so that I can go. Thanks!

Sorry for the last minute change to No. A bit sore from the ride last week in Ayer. Will still go, but will leave a little before or after the group at a much slower pace. Will be a great day to ride!
Sorry, can't make it.. I will join in on the next ride.
I just got off the waiting list for this ride, but I am no longer able to make it on Saturday. It is one of my favorites and I hope to do it another time.
I am a new member and I am looking forward to meeting all of you.
I'd also be interested in doing the longer ride.
Can't make it, enjoy the ride!
I've got two herniated disks in my back, so sadly I have to cancel. I hope you guys have a great ride!
Hoping to attend, if not, please email me how easy the biking was, i have a friend who would like to do it on our own if we cant attend with the meetup group
This is a great ride, if I can make and weather permitting I will. Quitos is a nice place with outdoor patio at the stop in Bristol-made other plans while on wait list; have fun!!
